      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah. and if it's all just a flicker, why do we have to keep fighting through the dark just to stay alive? it feels like we're just prolonging the inevitable. if the end result is always zero, then the struggle itself feels like a mistake. it's like we're choosing to stay in a room that's already on fire just because we're afraid to leave. wouldn't it be more logical to just... stop fighting it?",
